Class IdenticalUnitDefinitionFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.util.filters.IdenticalUnitDefinitionFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Filter

    public class IdenticalUnitDefinitionFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Filter
    This Filter only accepts instances of UnitDefinition that satisfy the method UnitDefinition.areIdentical(UnitDefinition, UnitDefinition).
